      <title>上议院投票推迟英国《卢旺达条约》对苏纳克的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/lords-vote-to-delay-uk-s-rwanda-treaty-in-blow-to-sunak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国上议院议员投票决定推迟英国向卢旺达派遣移民的有争议的计划，这一决定可能会激怒保守党右翼成员，并威胁到首相里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)关于在春季之前让飞机飞往这个非洲国家的誓言。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/lords-vote-to-delay-uk-s-rwanda-treaty-in-blow-to-sunak</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 21:04:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
